      "title": "Kota will return soon: Govt",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will return to the country soon. He didn't go into hiding. Cabinet Spokesperson Minister Bandula Gunawardena said that he will return to the country soon from Singapore."
      ],
